window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One great series in a single offering!</b></p> <p>The world is changing, and it needs a new Alpha. It needs me.</p> <p>I was doing well enough before the Apocalypse, but fast cars and penthouses mean nothing when the world changes into a wasteland filled with parasite-infested mutants.</p> <p>Now, the iron will that made me king of the boardroom is going to make me king of this new world. I am going to unlock my true power, I’m going to cultivate it, and I am going to dominate!</p>"; 
